snippet.textDisplay: Congratulations from Venezuela!!! Extraordinary, coherent and very complete explanation of another very important medical tool to help save lives...Many months ago, doctors in South Africa have reported the use of  FLUVOXAMINE to reduce the devastating effects of the cytokin attacks that create  blood clots (thrombi), that avoid oxígeno and nutrients from reaching the brain and all other vital organs, causing parálisis or death....
